# RabbitMQ Configuration
# For EuroEventos application to connect to RabbitMQ

# Option 1: Local development (RabbitMQ running on same machine)
# Using custom port: AMQP on 7770
RABBITMQ_URL=amqp://guest:guest@localhost:7770/

# Option 2: Docker network (if EuroEventos is also in Docker)
# RABBITMQ_URL=amqp://guest:guest@rabbitmq:5672/

# RabbitMQ Management UI (Web Interface)
# Access via: https://nuted-ia.dev/rabbitmq/
# Login: guest / guest
